      "user": "plagudocta",
      "slug": "liminal-spaces",
      "title": "Liminal Spaces",
      "desc": "\"There could be nostalgia, but where is everyone?\"\n\n\"Everything feels lost, like somewhere else, are we the only ones left here?\"\n\nThere may be at times people and backgrounds breathing in the back, but something feels detached.\n\nI feel like these films bring these sorts of emotions.\n\nMaybe you have some films that give you the same feelings too.",
